(2854, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'EVALUATING STARTUP IDEAS', 'The only true currency we humans have is time. Everybody is given a pot of time when they are born, and every day they take out a little from it. One dreaded day, the pot is empty.\nPeople will pay money to have a little more of that precious time...', '/post/evaluating-startup-ideas-82a', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:00 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2855, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'DO YOU NEED A CO-FOUNDER?', 'Co-founders are both the most important thing that your company needs and the most likely reason your company will fail. If you don’t have any co-founders, when you hit that dip, that speed bump along the road, you will be unable to continue...', '/post/do-you-need-a-co-founder-989', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:00 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2856, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'ARE YOU CAPABLE OF BEING RUTHLESS TO GET AHEAD?', 'A few years ago, I was consulting in the technical department of a big company that makes electronics. One day at a company party, a young guy about 24 years old, roughly my age, walked up to me and introduced himself...', '/post/are-you-capable-of-being-ruthless-to-get-ahead-259', 'Aug 26th, 2019 04:58 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2857, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'BUILD AROUND YOUR DISCOVERY MECHANISM', 'When you launch your web application, desktop software or any other type of software, the biggest problem you are going to face is very simple, but very hard to solve: People will not find your application...', '/post/build-around-your-discovery-mechanism-f7d', 'Aug 26th, 2019 04:57 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2858, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'HOW TO AVOID BEING A ONE-HIT WONDER', 'Most people, at some point, have a hit. Some hit blog post, some hit song, some hit startup, some great party and so on. But then that’s it. They try again, but it just doesn’t work the second time around...', '/post/how-to-avoid-being-a-one-hit-wonder-e90', 'Aug 26th, 2019 04:57 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2859, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'TWO YEARS IN THE TRENCHES BUILDING HOTELS.NG', 'Hotels.ng is about two years old now. In the first year, it was just a website — no business built around it. It started off by me purchasing lists of hotels. The entirety of hotels that were available in any known dataset that was available in public or in any government archive was about 1500 in Nigeria...', '/post/two-years-in-the-trenches-building-hotelsng-8e2', 'Aug 26th, 2019 04:54 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2860, 7, 'Mark Essien', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-d-CUw8-fyH0/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAT9k/EI_arUsjB04/photo.jpg', 'SHALLOW THINKING', 'It\'s quite easy to be good enough at something that everyone around you praises you. For example, you can read a few books, do a couple of courses and everyone will see you as a 3D printing guru. But that\'s mostly because nobody else knows anything about 3D...', '/post/shallow-thinking-908', 'Aug 26th, 2019 04:54 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
