(2865, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'My Internship Journey So Far', 'The Journey\nMy journey so has been much like a roller-coaster kind of feeling. But, let me tell you how it all started. So after registering for the internship, I did not get a welcome notification email immediately and that really made me think that I was not accepted...', '/post/my-internship-journey-so-far-5a8', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:31 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2866, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Class Day 1', '“Come to class, come to class, the lecturer is around (ooo)”. We know how the feeling is especially if it is the first day of class, the frantic desire and anxiety of not knowing how the class will turnout, how the lecturer will look like, how you are about to learn what your seniors are always talking about etc...', '/post/class-day-1-29a', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:31 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2867, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'My Experience In HTML', 'Learning and experimenting with Hypertext Markup Language (HTML) has been a big eye opener for me. As a starter in learning web development tools, I have come to know and appreciate the importance of HTML in building web and mobile app...', '/post/my-experience-in-html-2fd', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:31 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2868, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Lucid is back', 'We have taken time to work on a lot of issues listed by our users. Although Lucid is still very much a work in progress, we\'ve implemented a lot of sought after features, including the ability to edit and delete posts...', '/post/lucid-is-back-dc3', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:06 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2869, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Lucid is live', 'So we finally took lucid live. After spending so much time and pouring in a lot of effort into this, it\'s really refreshing to see a lot of people using it. Lots of positive feedback were received, especially commending the UI, ease of setting up an account and responsiveness...', '/post/lucid-is-live-d1a', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2870, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Hello New Followers', 'So I logged into Lucid today and noticed a x10 increase in followers. Welcome guys, hope you are enjoying Lucid so far', '/post/hello-new-followers-b24', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2871, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'New features incoming', 'So new Lucid users, we have so much amazing stuff coming soon. We\'re working constantly to fix various bugs and some much anticipated features will debut soon. Stay tuned and keep enjoying Lucid', '/post/new-features-incoming-e0a', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2872, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'How did your day go?', 'As Prosper Otemuyiwa would say &quot;A new day, another opportunity to be world class&quot;.\nIt\'s a new day, what were you able to achieve today? Mine was quite stressful, but there was a cool win for me...', '/post/how-did-your-day-go-4cb', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2873, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Working round the clock on Lucid', 'We went live some days back, and the amount of positive feedback we\'ve gotten is amazing. Really heart warming stuff.\nThough, naturally there\'s the other side of the coin. The bugs and incomplete features...', '/post/working-round-the-clock-on-lucid-a0b', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2874, 3, 'Jeffrey Ogah', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-FQgpN5l_UoY/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAARA/YF9rc3luwuw/photo.jpg', 'Stressful Day', 'Its been a while since I was stressed this much. Went to bed by 6am, got back up by 10am and still yet to get any sleep. I\'m a sucker for working hard, so I find it difficult to rest easy when there\'s work to be done...', '/post/stressful-day-a65', 'Aug 26th, 2019 05:02 PM', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
