art of this and get full internship as we go along.\n\nWe meet at the top!!!\n\n  \n\n  \n\n![](/storage/1802/images/img-bmesy7axtw.png)![](/storage/1802/images/img-ch00e678rk.png)', 'HTML, STARTNG, CODING, CV', 'what-i-have-done-so-far-on-startng-8c8', '2019-08-26 03:48:50', '2019-08-28 10:30:05', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL),
