(316, 506, 'What I have learnt so far on StartNG pre-internship', 'As someone that is not a beginner n coding, I would say the most significant thing I have learnt so far from this program i image and video hosting service by Cloudinary. Before now, I used Imgur to host remote images for my projects or pushed said images to Github but now I am intrigued by what I can do with capabilities Cloudinary provides. An example of this can be seen here: [ ](https://res.cloudinary.com/ddlh0vis5/image/upload/v1566822882/task-2-challenge_dyoimt.png)[https://res.cloudinary.com/ddlh0vis5/image/upload/v1566822882/task-2-challenge\\_dyoimt.png](https://res.cloudinary.com/ddlh0vis5/image/upload/v1566822882/task-2-challenge_dyoimt.png) . I am really looking forward to using Cloudinary in my future projects', NULL, 'what-i-have-learnt-so-far-on-startng-pre-internship-ef1', '2019-08-26 15:08:49', '2019-08-28 10:30:14', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
