(382, 834, 'startNG Task 2', '**THE HTML TEST.**\n\nlearning web development has been on thing i have always looked forward to. Thanks to StartNg program, its been a big progress. I got to understand how HTML works and all the basis i needed to know was thought to us. The first task on Web page containing our CV using HTML and its been a successful one. Thanks StartNG.\n\n![](/storage/834/images/img-r18yf61h47.png)', NULL, 'startng-task-2-3b1', '2019-08-26 18:10:30', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(383, 1591, 'My HNG Internship Journey So far', '<p> </p>\n<p>Hmm! It’s only been a few days since the internship started and I must say, speed is of the essence!</p>\n<p>One of the things I’ve picked up very quickly is that rules are very important, we either stick to them or get kicked out...', '', 'my-hng-internship-journey-so-far-693', '2019-08-26 18:20:43', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', 'imohessiet/images/img-6v9wzxc9y.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(384, 2238, 'My Experience so far', 'I am really appreciative to the friends that share to the knowledge that as brought me to writing this post. The post and process is turning out to be an engaging and a very enlightening adventure. I would love to have better and deeper knowledge of html about the inner working of all the processes that brought me here. Most importantly i will love to be an excellent developer.', NULL, 'my-experience-so-far-2c0', '2019-08-26 18:28:21', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(385, 2212, 'USING HTML', 'I joined a newbie and I\'m really ecstatic to be able to have been able to create this html file. I can\'t believe I did this. It was super gratifying to build this & I got a kick out of adding colors. I truly cannot wait to see what else I can come up with. Thank you so much.\n\n![](/storage/2212/images/img-b8ytzlmwgh.png)', NULL, 'using-html-dd2', '2019-08-26 18:34:31', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(386, 2141, 'HTML', 'So far so good, HTML, which stands for Hypertext Markup Language is the language of the web. Just the way documents are presented on Microsoft word, documents can also be presented on the web by means of HTML. Various element like heading, topics, subtopics, tables paragraphs, image can be displayed appropriately on the web by appropriate codes and syntax written in the HTML environment. Below is a snapshot of the HTML code and the corresponding output.\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n![](/storage/2141/images/img-ux5hq36gir.png)\r\n\r\n  \r\n\r\n![](/storage/2141/images/img-vhzumbeoea.png)', NULL, 'html-05a', '2019-08-26 18:35:05', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(387, 2141, 'the STARTNG class so far', '<p><strong>WHAT I HAVE LEARNED SO FAR</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>I have learnt how to create a blog post and link it. I have been exposed to various sites and its importance</li>\n<li>I have also learnt practically the importance of belonging to groups</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>IMPROVEMENTS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>seek for a better way to carry everyone along</li>\n<li>information being passed are not explicit and organised</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>WHAT I WANT TO LEARN</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>to develop software, especially GIS software...', '', 'the-startng-class-so-far-8a9', '2019-08-26 18:35:05', '2019-08-28 10:30:17', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(388, 168, 'I Can Code', '<p>I have been able to understand Most of the basics of HTML in this internship program and with the knowledge I\'ve created my CV using HTML. Below is what I\'ve done as touching the task.</p>\n<p>Surprisingly, I have created my first HTML page from the lessons we\'ve been taught on start...', '', 'i-can-code-7b6', '2019-08-26 18:42:00', '2019-08-28 10:30:18', 'danieloladimeji04/images/img-aanbigmbvi.png', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(389, 168, 'The Pre-Internship Tour', '<p>Start.ng is a nice abode for all beginners out there.....</p>\n<p>My adventure on start.ng has been a great one thus far with the help of our well trained and welcoming mentors \'shoutout to them\'. So the first task given to us is as thus</p>\n<ol>\n<li>What I\'ve learnt so far:</li>\n<li>What i wish to learn and</li>\n<li>what i wished to be improved</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>What i\'ve learnt so far</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>i\'ve learnt on surviving the internship course: our mentors have helped by giving us some articles and write ups that\'ll help improve your adaptation and survival</li>\n<li>using slack: also with the help of the mentors i have been able to use the slack app effectively</li>\n<li>notes: i was also taught on how to create notes on the slack app for reference purposes</li>\n<li>ive learnt how to open a github profile</li>\n<li>also i\'ve been taught on how to access and make use of developer tools on the google chrome appp</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What i wish to learn</strong></p>\n<p>aside from the main courses</p>\n<p>i hope to acquire good communication skills and improve my intelligence on interactions</p>\n<p><strong>What i wish to be improved</strong></p>\n<p>during this tour ive not actually seen any flaw in the program...', '', 'the-pre-internship-tour-d8d', '2019-08-26 18:42:00', '2019-08-28 10:30:18', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(390, 168, 'Task', '<p>Hello world,</p>\n<p>As a pre-intern at start.ng I have learnt a lot of things since the last few days</p>\n<p>*Surviving the internship; how you\'ll survive by interacting with others, following instructions, looking out for others and some hints on becoming what you really want</p>\n<p>I wish to learn Html, Css &amp; Javascript during the program</p>\n<p>I wish organizing the interns could be improved to avoid unnecessary posts</p>', '', 'task-c98', '2019-08-26 18:42:00', '2019-08-28 10:30:18', '', NULL, NULL, NULL);
