(545, 2265, 'Start NG Questionnaire', '<p>What you have Learned so far:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>On HTML:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I have learnt the diffrrent tags</p>\n<p>Forms</p>\n<p>Medias</p>\n<p>Adding Images</p>\n<p>Text Fields</p>\n<ul>\n<li>On Css:</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Meaning of CSS</p>\n<p>CSS Selectors</p>\n<p>Groupings</p>\n<p>CSS Pseudo - Classes</p>\n<p>Css Values</p>\n<p>Cascade</p>\n<p>What You Wish to Learn:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>I wish to learn Andriod development</li>\n<li>Back end development</li>\n</ul>\n<p>What you wish should be improved</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The timing is not too comfortable as some people are workers and do not have much time during the day</li>\n<li>Also, there should be a group for information only, and only the admin can comment there, so that when ever information is needed, people can refer to that link to avoid lots of chats from people...', '', 'start-ng-questionnaire-6c1', '2019-08-27 05:14:03', '2019-08-28 10:30:26', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
