(692, 311, 'Daffodils', '<p>I wandered lonely as a cloud</p>\n<p>That floats on high o\'er vales and hills,</p>\n<p>When all at once I saw a crowd,</p>\n<p>A host, of golden daffodils;</p>\n<p>Beside the lake, beneath the trees,</p>\n<p>Fluttering and dancing in the breeze...', '', 'daffodils-7e5', '2019-08-27 10:02:00', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(693, 329, 'My Journey on HTML', '<p>Using the Hyper Text Markup Language (HTML) has been super cool with HNG.</p>\n<p>I have learnt to arrange elements into header, body and footer elements.</p>\n<p>I learnt to define structures using headings (h1 to h6), paragraphs(p) when needed...', '', 'my-journey-on-html-ce5', '2019-08-27 10:14:33', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', 'topejoan2/images/img-q8lju377v8.png', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(694, 329, 'My learning so far', '<p>So far, have learnt how to optimally use Slack. This community has broadened my knowledge in understanding HTML5 and its elements.</p>\n<p>I wish to go further in this training learning more of front end and having technical know-how on back end too...', '', 'my-learning-so-far-56f', '2019-08-27 10:14:33', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(695, 256, 'StartNG: My Experience', '<p>A child that craves ice cream and have always looked for means to get it, will enjoy every bit of it when he lays his hands on it. That\'s the feeling i had when i had a class on my first language during the pre internship organized by Star...', '', 'startng-my-experience-296', '2019-08-27 10:18:54', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', 'umehvictormario/images/img-aqx6fpg5px.png', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(696, 256, 'STARTNG INTERNSHIP', '<p>I started a pre-internship on StartNG on the 19th of August and in that little time I learned a lot. I joined an amazing community and it was like I was introduced to an arena where you need to be on your toes at all time...', '', 'startng-internship-1da', '2019-08-27 10:18:54', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(697, 132, 'MY HTML JOURNEY', '<p>Going on this html journey has had its different experiences, from using VS Code editor to write html codes for my CV. I have known html element tags, creating tables without borders.</p>\n<p>HTML has shows organization, how coordinated your code is makes your coding environment attractive and easy to glance or read through...', '', 'my-html-journey-4e7', '2019-08-27 10:19:27', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', 'adurajoshua/images/img-29muaq8hte.png', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(698, 132, 'My StartNG Internship', '<p>Joining the STARTNG PreInternship has been first challenging, getting used to the Slack app, but it\'s been interesting all the while.</p>\n<p>I have learnt:</p>\n<p>1, I need to follow instructions none the less what I may see others do</p>\n<p>2...', '', 'my-startng-internship-dd1', '2019-08-27 10:19:27', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', '', NULL, NULL, NULL),
(699, 2279, 'DOCUMENTING MY JOURNEY SO FAR WITH START.NG', '<p>Big thank you to <strong>Start.Ng</strong> for giving me the opportunity to learn how to write a few lines of code. It\'s surprisingly shocking to me how I transited from being a stack novice into understanding how to utilize one of the widely used markup languages; HTML...', '', 'documenting-my-journey-so-far-with-startng-ec5', '2019-08-27 10:22:30', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', 'bassey.utibe22/images/img-d597tm8it5.png', NULL, NULL, NULL),
