(701, 2279, 'WHAT I HAVE LEARNT SO FAR ON SLACK', '<p>Hello my name is Bassey Utibe and I would like to document my experience on the SLACK platform.</p>\n<p>WHAT I HAVE LEARNT SO FAR</p>\n<ol>\n<li>i learnt that programming can be learnt by anyone who wishes to</li>\n<li>I have learnt the basic fundamentals of HTML, CSS, JS, GIT, PHP etc</li>\n</ol>\n<p>I also wish get more hands-on knowledge in digital marketing...', '', 'what-i-have-learnt-so-far-on-slack-24f', '2019-08-27 10:22:30', '2019-08-28 10:30:34', '', NULL, NULL, NULL);
